## Summary

| Area | Current State | Target State |
|---|---|---|
| **Data flow** | Dual-write (counter + row) | Single atomic event INSERT |
| **Idempotency** | None | Client-generated UUID + UNIQUE constraint |
| **Daily count** | Independent counter on `user_profiles` | Derived: `COUNT(*) WHERE date = today` |
| **Analytics depth** | Right/Wrong + time | Session, engagement, source bucket, hesitation signals |
| **Query performance** | Full scan on every page load | Trigger-maintained daily aggregates |
| **Audit capability** | None | Full event log, immutable, queryable |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The highest-priority fix is **Phase 1** — the idempotency guard and atomic RPC. This alone will eliminate ghost data for new answers going forward. Phases 2-4 build the intelligence layer on top of a now-trustworthy foundation.
